<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: rgb(250, 94, 224);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: rgb(250, 94, 224);
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
           <h1>
             Hello <%= firstName %>!
           </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
        <hr>
        <h2>Vendor Application Status</h2>
        <p>Thank you for submitting your vendor application to Nana's Pourfection Hub!</p>
        <p>We have received your application and it is currently under review by our admin team.</p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> Pending Approval</p>
        <p>We will notify you via email as soon as your application has been reviewed. This typically takes 0-2 business days.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                This email was sent by Nana's Pourfection Hub &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>